      <p>After almost two decades since the foundation of our second hand bikes shop in Berlin, we are expanding our business to online shopping. Now you are able to buy our quality new and used bicycles from the comfort of your home.<br></p>
      <p class="mobile-hidden">Register and become part of a big Bike Berlin’s community. You’ll be able to offer your own used bicycle to our customers and you’ll have a numerous discounts on reparations and other products in our offer.<br>
      In future we hope to expand our online product pallette to include complete used cycling goods that we offer in our shop.</p>
